  <scopecontent id="aspace_d89e51ca548538096295c39619c110b4">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p><head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head> Will of William Griffith, Sr., of the Indiana Territory, and indentures for land bought or sold in Indiana; also family Bible and other genealogical data on Griffith and related families, including Alkin, Barnes, Clark, Ewing, Hays, Henkle [Hinkle], Horback, Hungerford, Hunt, Landes, Pierce, Squires, Van Camp, and White families.</p><p> Griffith Family. Papers, #2062. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.</p>  </scopecontent>
